	<ThingDef ParentName="BaseMeleeWeapon_Sharp_Quality">
		<defName>GW_SM_Melee_FlameSword</defName>
		<label>Emperor's sword</label>
		<description>The Emperor's Sword is a giant, flaming sword that was created and wielded by the God-Emperor of Mankind Himself. Not only can no armor withstand its sundering stroke, but His blade can also destroy daemons permanently, instead of merely banishing them back to the Warp.\n\nThousands of daemons were felled by this blade, and thousands more were felled by Roboute Guilliman, the Imperial Regent, who wielded the Emperor's Sword during the Thirteenth Black Crusade of the 41st Millennium.\n\nOf course, this blade is a mere replica - a fine one it is, but the true Emperor's Sword and its wielder are too important to leave Terra except for the most imperative tasks.</description>
		<possessionCount>1</possessionCount>
